Download Android SDK (ADT Bundle):
http://developer.android.com/sdk/index.html#download

e.g. Linux 32-bit:
http://dl.google.com/android/adt/adt-bundle-linux-x86-20130514.zip

Unpack sdk
unzip adt-bundle-linux-x86-20130514.zip

Start Eclipse
cd adt-bundle-linux-x86/ecplise
./eclipse

Import Project
File -> Import -> Android -> Existing Android Code Into Workspace

Root Directory: android/examples/misc/HelloWorld -> Finish

Device 
http://developer.android.com/tools/device.html